Title: NETMESSAGE:ROLL OUT
NETMESSAGE:Move between rotating rings to avoid falling into the slime!
Translation: 在旋转的圆环之间闪转腾挪，不要掉到黏液里！

Title: NETMESSAGE:PERFECT MATCH
NETMESSAGE:Match the icon on the screen to avoid the slime!
Translation: 和屏幕上的标志匹配上就能避开黏液！

Title: NETMESSAGE:STOMPIN' GROUND
NETMESSAGE:Avoid the charging Rhinos and stay inside the area!
Translation: 躲避横冲直撞的犀牛，尽量留在场地内！

Title: NETMESSAGE:BLOCK PARTY
NETMESSAGE:Avoid the moving walls and stay on the platform!
Translation: 闪避向你冲来的墙面，留在平台上吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:JUMP CLUB
NETMESSAGE:Jump over the spinning beam and avoid falling into the slime!
Translation: 跳过旋转的横杆，不要掉进黏液里！

Title: NETMESSAGE:SLIME CLIMB
NETMESSAGE:Outrun the slime and reach the finish line!
Translation: 逃过上涨的岩浆，躲过各类障碍，冲向终点吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:THE WHIRLYGIG
NETMESSAGE:Navigate the obstacles and race to the finish line!
Translation: 避开障碍物冲向终点吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:SEE SAW
NETMESSAGE:Run and balance across rows of see-saws to reach the finish line!
Translation: 跑过一个又一个跷跷板，保持平衡，冲向终点线！

Title: NETMESSAGE:DOOR DASH
NETMESSAGE:Avoid the fake doors and race to the finish line!
NETMESSAGE:TIP TOE
NETMESSAGE:Avoid the fake tiles and find the hidden path to reach the finish line!
Translation: 避开假的地砖，找到通往终点线的隐藏路径吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:GATE CRASH
NETMESSAGE:Avoid the moving doors and race to the finish line!
Translation: 避开移动的门，冲向终点吧！

Title: NETMESSAGE:HEX-A-GONE
NETMESSAGE:Be the last Fall Guy standing above the slime!
Translation: 勇敢成为最后一个不沾黏液的糖豆人吧！
